<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thoughts - Forget Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f0ff;
            color: #4a148c;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .forget-container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 350px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .forget-container h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #6a1b9a;
        }

        .forget-container p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .forget-container input[type="email"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #d1c4e9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a148c;
        }

        .forget-container input[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #6a1b9a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .forget-container input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #4a148c;
        }

        .forget-container .login-link {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7e57c2;
        }

        .forget-container .login-link a {
            color: #6a1b9a;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .forget-container .login-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="forget-container">
        <h2>Ohh! Forgot Password?</h2>
        <p>Don't worry, we got you. Enter your email below to reset your password.</p>
        <form action="/forget" method="POST">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
            <input type="submit" value="Send Reset Link">
        </form>
        <div class="login-link">
            <p>Remembered your password? <a href="/login">Login here</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
